OL,3,CWhen will the rain return? UK heatwave
OL,4,Cand dry spell set to continue
OL,6,FAs the UK endures its third heatwave
OL,7,Fof the year, there is little sign of
OL,8,Fany significant rainfall in the near
OL,9,Ffuture, according to the Met Office.
OL,11,FThe prolonged spell of hot, dry
OL,12,Fweather has already led to hosepipe
OL,13,Fbans across parts of England and
OL,14,Fcontributed to 19 wildfires this month.
OL,16,FScientists have also estimated that at
OL,17,Fleast 2,700 deaths across the UK were
OL,18,Flinked to the extreme heat seen during
OL,19,FMay and June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
