FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784134075
OL,3,CWhen will the rain return? UK heatwave
OL,4,Cand dry spell set to continue
OL,6,FThe average temperature for July 2025
OL,7,Fwas 16.8C, almost half the temperature
OL,8,Fwe are seeing at the moment.
OL,10,FLast year's July rainfall was 10% less
OL,11,Fthan average, with Dorset recording
OL,12,Fless than half of its average.
OL,14,FHow does the rest of July look?
OL,16,FThe Met Office said there is a higher
OL,17,Fchance of rain in the latter part of
OL,18,Fthe month, with showers and
OL,19,Fthunderstorms possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
