FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784134075
OL,3,CWhen will the rain return? UK heatwave
OL,4,Cand dry spell set to continue
OL,6,FWhen, where and how much rain there
OL,7,Fwill be is unclear yet.
OL,9,FThis does not necessarily mean the
OL,10,Fclassic wet British weather is back
OL,11,Ffor good, but more that there will be
OL,12,Fa variety of weather hitting the UK,
OL,13,Fwith sunshine continuing.
OL,15,FHopefully this will leave things
OL,16,Ffeeling slightly cooler and crops will
OL,17,Fget a much needed drink.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
